</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-55BECD2D-C3FF-4E08-B52A-597FAB1BE48B" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Overview</title><fig id="GUID-0E1DD21C-4761-4E76-8B1B-A08792631661" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-CBF9A935-05C5-4D83-A78B-520A636AAFF9-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CBF9A935-05C5-4D83-A78B-520A636AAFF9-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BD979D72-1928-42AF-96D2-4AFFDD5DEA1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">The different options</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Customer fix</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The customer can solve his problem on his own. He probably uses user guides and or maintenance actions. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Remote fix</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The customer is helped via a call to the help desk. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">You will find an overview of the available tools for the help desk in this document: 
<xref keyref="Helpdesk_tools" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-BD5329CE-8C8D-4E35-896C-092E52035617.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text Helpdesk tools?>Helpdesk tools</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">On site fix</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">A technician needs to go to the customer to fix the error. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">You will find an overview of the available tools for the service technician in this document: 
<xref keyref="Service_tools" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-2F88B95D-16BC-42B7-A2AD-A9FEE37FFE46.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text Element ID :GUID-2F88B95D-16BC-42B7-A2AD-A9FEE37FFE46?>Service tools</xref> 
</p></li></ol></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-926475FC-2290-4598-98DD-0D62BDEABBE4.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Service operations</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
